	<transcript sound="intro"><![CDATA[Welcome to module 4.<br /><br />In this module we will be looking at contamination hazards. <br /><br />We will learn what contamination hazards are, how they transfer to food and how to control them.<br /><br />Let's first learn the meaning of a few terms related to contamination.<br /><br />Click a term on the left and then match it to its meaning by clicking on a definition, then click 'Check Answer'.]]></transcript>
	
	<transcript sound="soundcorrect"><![CDATA[You are right! Take a minute to study the definitions again before clicking ‘Next’ to proceed.]]></transcript>
